---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const title = 'Disclaimer';
const description = 'Important disclaimer regarding financial, legal, and professional advice on Hustle Teacher.';
import "../styles/starwind.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={title} description={description} />
	</head>
	<body class="bg-background text-foreground scheme-dark min-h-screen flex flex-col">
		<Header />
		<main class="flex-grow docs-site-container border-x">
			<article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
				<h1>Disclaimer</h1>
				<p class="text-muted-foreground"><strong>Last Updated: March 9, 2026</strong></p>

				<h2>⚠️ Important Legal Disclaimer</h2>
				<p>
					Please read this disclaimer carefully. By accessing and using Hustle Teacher, you acknowledge that you have read,
					understood, and agree to be bound by this disclaimer.
				</p>

				<h2>1. No Professional Advice</h2>
				<p>
					<strong>Hustle Teacher provides educational content only.</strong> We do not provide:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Financial advice or investment recommendations</li>
					<li>Legal advice or guidance</li>
					<li>Tax advice or accounting services</li>
					<li>Medical or health advice</li>
					<li>Professional consulting services</li>
				</ul>
				<p>
					Always consult with qualified professionals (financial advisors, attorneys, tax professionals) before making any
					decisions based on content found on our site.
				</p>

				<h2>2. Educational Purposes Only</h2>
				<p>
					All content on Hustle Teacher is provided for educational and informational purposes only. The information is
					based on our research and personal experience, but is not guaranteed to be accurate, complete, or up-to-date.
				</p>

				<h2>3. No Guarantee of Results</h2>
				<p>
					Income, earnings, and success from online ventures vary widely. Results depend on many factors including your
					effort, skill level, market conditions, and timing. Past performance or examples do not guarantee future results.
				</p>
				<p>
					<strong>Earnings Disclaimer:</strong> Any specific earnings claims or income examples are not meant to be an
					average. Your results may vary significantly based on individual factors.
				</p>

				<h2>4. Affiliate Relationships & Sponsored Content</h2>
				<p>
					Hustle Teacher may include affiliate links to products and services we recommend. If you click an affiliate link
					and make a purchase, we may receive a commission at no additional cost to you. This helps support our site.
				</p>
				<p>
					We only recommend products and services we believe in, but we encourage you to do your own research before
					purchasing.
				</p>

				<h2>5. No Liability</h2>
				<p>
					Hustle Teacher, its authors, and contributors are not liable for any damages, losses, or consequences arising from
					your use of this site or reliance on its content. This includes but is not limited to:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Financial losses or investment losses</li>
					<li>Lost income or business losses</li>
					<li>Direct or indirect damages</li>
					<li>Consequential or incidental damages</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>6. Links to Third-Party Sites</h2>
				<p>
					Hustle Teacher is not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of linked third-party websites. We do
					not endorse external sites, and your use of them is at your own risk.
				</p>

				<h2>7. User Responsibility</h2>
				<p>
					You are solely responsible for your use of this site and any decisions made based on its content. It is your
					responsibility to:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Verify information from reliable sources</li>
					<li>Consult professionals before making major decisions</li>
					<li>Understand the risks involved in any venture</li>
					<li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>8. Accuracy of Information</h2>
				<p>
					While we strive to provide accurate and current information, errors may occur. We do not warrant that any
					information on our site is accurate, complete, or free from errors. Information is subject to change without notice.
				</p>

				<h2>9. No Warranty</h2>
				<p>
					All content is provided "as is" without any warranties, either express or implied. We make no representations or
					warranties regarding merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, or non-infringement.
				</p>

				<h2>10. Changes to This Disclaimer</h2>
				<p>
					We may update this disclaimer at any time without notice. Your continued use of the site following any changes
					constitutes your acceptance of the new disclaimer.
				</p>

				<h2>11. Assumption of Risk</h2>
				<p>
					By using Hustle Teacher, you assume all risks associated with your use of the site and acknowledge that you have
					read and understood this disclaimer in its entirety.
				</p>

				<h2>12. Governing Law</h2>
				<p>
					This disclaimer shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable law, without regard to conflicts of
					law principles.
				</p>

				<h2>13. Contact Us</h2>
				<p>
					If you have questions about this disclaimer, please contact us at:
					<br />
					<strong>Email:</strong> contact@hustleteacher.com
				</p>

				<hr class="border-t border-border my-8" />

				<p class="text-center text-sm text-muted-foreground">
					<strong>Last Reminder:</strong> Conduct thorough research and consult with professionals before making any important
					decisions.
				</p>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
